results.deck: Yuke's Co. is a Japanese developer. It is best known for numerous WWE games, as well as the UFC Undisputed franchise.
results.description:
Overview

Yuke's Co.'s first World Wrestling Entertainment video game was WWF SmackDown! in 2000. Since then, they have developed almost all of the games for the WWE, and THQ has published them. THQ and Yuke's have also partnered with the Ultimate Fighting Championship to create the UFC Undisputed games. Aside from WWE and UFC, they also created Wrestle Kingdom in their native Japan, which features popular Japanese wrestlers.
